p: To the Sheriff or any Constable of said County James Hughes. J.B. Webber R. J. Moores Thos Talentul Hanson John Madden Richard McCaan Rb Caldron Marty Faby

You are hereby notified to be and appear before the undersigned one of the Justices of the Peace in and for Said County Wt Ty Office in Steilacoom Justice then and there to give Evidance in a Case to be tried Wherein the Territory of Washington is Plaintiff and James Riley is defendant in the past of De ft
Given under my hand this the 1st day of March AD 1861
